org.ncgr.pubmed

Class PubMedSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ncgr.pubmed.PubMedSummary

  • public class PubMedSummary
extends java.lang.Object
    A reader that parses a PubMed eSummaryResult XML response. Results are stored in public instance variables rather than getters.
    Author:
    Sam Hokin
